blueprint.label: Solar Parts Block
blueprint.description:
Builds solar panals and accumulators, both vanilla and Advanced Solar:
https://mods.factorio.com/mod/Advanced-Electric-Revamped-v16

Center array produces 11.4MW sustained (both day & night).  Extra 15% accumulators.  If they drop below 15%, blackout is imminent!  (Create an alert for this.)

Use upgrade planner to increase that 10x, 100x, or 1000x.  Old parts will be automatically recycled.

Add "Solar Supply" to the Construction Train directly after Red Mall Supply, condition "inactivity 1s".
